Comment: I really like this opening move.
Black's next move will probably be e5, I think at this point.
Threatening his knight with my bishop
Opening a path for my DSB.
He makes the move that I foresaw four moves ago.
For some reason, instead of taking my pawn, instead, he takes out the bishop.
I continue to attack with my pawn.
He takes it (but now I have a one-point advantage).
